						 <p>COLLABCOON WOOO</p> <p>This is a collaboration between <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ihp" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1267048&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1561382331" alt="Ihp" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1267048)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ihp" >Ihp</a></span> and myself for collab con featuring the Chicago Spirit and Factory. By the way, this is a GoI Format double feature, so there's a good chance you missed half of the story.</p> <p>Chicago Spirit Format: <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/fragment:chicago-factory-1">http://www.scp-wiki.net/fragment:chicago-factory-1</a><br /> Factory Format: <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/fragment:chicago-factory-2">http://www.scp-wiki.net/fragment:chicago-factory-2</a></p> <p>image salsa: <a href="https://www.loc.gov/item/89706120/">https://www.loc.gov/item/89706120/</a></p> <p>Special thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3440103&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1561382331" alt="Captain Kirby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3440103)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" >Captain Kirby</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rounderhouse" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4187885&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1561382331" alt="Rounderhouse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4187885)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rounderhouse" >Rounderhouse</a></span> for their invaluable crit.</p> 
				 	]]>
